############################################
# The omicsList object is a list of lists. Each top level represents a different omics type.
#
# omicsList[[i]][[1]] "dataType" is the name of the omics set
# omicsList[[i]][[2]] "dataFormat" is the data format of the omics set.
# omicsList[[i]][[3]] "filename" is the filename/path for the omics data set.
# omicsList[[i]][[4]] "RawData" is the raw data.
# omicsList[[i]][[5]] "eSet" is the working eset object
# omicsList[[i]][[6]] "topVariable" is the index of the most variable features
# omicsList[[i]][[7]] "fit" is the limmaFit output of eBayes
# omicsList[[i]][[8]]
# omicsList[[i]][[9]] 
# omicsList[[i]][[10]] "siteNorm" is  data normalized to the first data set by protein or gene
# omicsList[[i]][[11]] 
# omicsList[[i]][[12]] "prebatch_eset" is the normalized but pre-batch corrected eset, if applicable
# omicsList[[i]][[14]] is the un-normalized eset object - for debugging only
#
############################################

# Make index variables
metab_data_index <- c();  # index of all Metabolite data
mz_data_index <- c();     # index of all data with mz
phos_data_index <- c();   # index of Phospho Site Data (from MQ)
sites_data_index <- c();  # index of all site data (from MQ)
data_norm_index <- c();  # index of site data normalized to proteome (if applicable)
gene_data_index <- c();   # index of all data  with Gene (HGNC Symbols)
prot_data_index <- c();   # index of all data with Protein (Uniprot IDs)
prot_groups_index <- c(); # index of all Protein Groups Data (MQ)
unnorm_gene_index<-c() # index of all data with Genes, including pre-site normalized

# Import annotation file
if(!file.exists(annotation_filename)){
  print(paste("Annotation file not found: ",annotation_filename,sep=""))
  stop()    
}
annot <- data.frame(openxlsx::read.xlsx(annotation_filename, 1, colNames=FALSE)); # read annotation
contrastgroups <- unique(gsub("\\.","", make.names(na.omit(t(annot[1,-1:-3])))) );
annot<-annot[c(-1,-4),];

# Make omicsList object
omicsList <- vector("list", (nrow(annot)-2) )

for (i in 1:(nrow(annot)-2) ){
  omicsList[[i]] <- vector("list", 14);
  omicsList[[i]][1] <- make.names(annot[i+2,1]);
  names(omicsList[[i]])[1] <- gsub("\\.","", make.names("dataType"));
  omicsList[[i]][2] <- make.names(annot[i+2,2]);
  names(omicsList[[i]])[2] <- "dataFormat";
  if(grepl("Metabolites", omicsList[[i]][["dataFormat"]]) ){ metab_data_index <- c(metab_data_index, i)  };
  if(omicsList[[i]][["dataFormat"]]=="Phospho.Sites..MQ."){ phos_data_index <- c(phos_data_index, i)  };
  if(any(omicsList[[i]][["dataFormat"]] %in% c("Protein.Groups..MQ.", "Peptides..MQ.")) ){ prot_groups_index <- c(prot_groups_index, i) };
  if(grepl(".Sites..MQ.",omicsList[[i]][["dataFormat"]]) ){ sites_data_index <- c(sites_data_index, i)  };
  omicsList[[i]][[3]] <- annot[i+2,3];
  names(omicsList[[i]])[3] <- "filename";
}

# Format annotation table
annot[3:nrow(annot),3] <- annot[3:nrow(annot),1];
annot <- t(annot[,-1:-2]);

  omicsList[[i]][[4]] <- data.frame(read.delim(omicsList[[i]][[3]], header=TRUE, stringsAsFactors=FALSE,
                                               sep=file_ext_sep, check.names=FALSE));
  names(omicsList[[i]])[4] <- "RawData";
  
  tryCatch({
    
    omicsList[[i]][[5]] <- makeEset(data=omicsList[[i]][[4]], annotate=annot, type=omicsList[[i]][[1]], 
                                    log_transform=log_transform,
                                    data_format=omicsList[[i]][[2]], uniprot_annotation=query_web);
    }, error=function(e){
      stop(paste("Problem with input data format:", e));
    })
  
  names(omicsList[[i]])[5] <- "eSet";
  if(debug_opt == TRUE ) { omicsList[[i]][[14]] <- omicsList[[i]][[5]] }# use for debugging
    
  if( "Gene" %in% colnames(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])) ) { gene_data_index <- c(gene_data_index, i) };
  if( "Protein" %in% colnames(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])) ) { prot_data_index <- c(prot_data_index, i) };
  if( "mz" %in% colnames(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])) ) { mz_data_index <- c(mz_data_index, i) };
}

Data Normalization

pca_output <- vector("list", length(omicsList) )
output_links<-"";

for(i in 1:length(omicsList)){
  if(length(zero_percent)==1){use_zero<-zero_percent}else{use_zero<-zero_percent[i]}
  if(length(norm_method)==1){use_norm<-norm_method}else{use_norm<-norm_method[i]}
  
  if(debug_opt){ index<-14 } else { index <- 5 }
  omicsList[[i]][[5]] <-intensityNorm(eset=omicsList[[i]][[index]],
                                      type=omicsList[[i]][[1]], 
                                      data_format=omicsList[[i]][["dataFormat"]],
                                      norm=norm_method, zero_cutoff=zero_percent,
                                      min_feature=min_feature_per_sample,
                                      norm_by_batch=norm_batches)
  
  
  # Make output hyperlinks for markdown
  add_link <- paste(omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]], ": [ Boxplot/Dist. ](", output_plots_subdir,
                    "/boxplot_histogram_",omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]],".pdf)", sep="")
  output_links <- paste(output_links, add_link, sep="" )
  
  # Batch correction
  if("Batch" %in% colnames(pData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])) & !("Met" %in% omicsList[[i]][["dataFormat"]])) { try({
    suppressPackageStartupMessages({require(sva) });
    suppressMessages({ suppressWarnings({
    omicsList[[i]][[12]] <- omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]]
    names(omicsList[[i]])[12] <- "prebatch_eset"
    
    pheno = pData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])
    edata = exprs(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])
    batch = pheno$Batch
  
    modcombat = model.matrix(~1, data=pheno)
    combat_edata = ComBat(dat=edata, batch=batch, mod=modcombat, par.prior=TRUE, prior.plots=FALSE)
    combat_eset = ExpressionSet(assayData=combat_edata)
    pData(combat_eset) = pData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])
    fData(combat_eset) = fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])
    })})
    omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]] <- combat_eset
    tmp<-drawPCA(eset=omicsList[[i]][["prebatch_eset"]], type=paste(omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]],"_precorrection", sep=""));
    
    capture.output( intensityNorm(eset=omicsList[[i]][[index]],
                                      type=paste(omicsList[[i]][[1]],"_postBatchCor",sep=""), 
                                      data_format=omicsList[[i]][["dataFormat"]],
                                      norm=norm_post_batch, zero_cutoff=zero_percent,
                                      min_feature=min_feature_per_sample, norm_by_batch=F) )
    
  }) }
  
  if(remove_group!=""){
    omicsList[[i]][[5]] <- omicsList[[i]][[5]][, !grepl(paste(remove_group, collapse="|"),pData(omicsList[[i]][[5]])$Group) ]
  }
  
  try({
  # PCA plots
  pca_output[[i]] <- drawPCA(eset=omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]], type=omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]])
  
  # Make output hyperlinks for markdown
  add_link <- paste( "[ PCA ](", output_plots_subdir,"/PCAplots_",omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]],".pdf)", sep="")
  output_links <- paste(output_links, add_link, sep=" | " )
  })
  try({ 
    drawUMAP(eset=omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]], type=omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]])
    add_link <- paste( "[ UMAP ](", output_plots_subdir,"/UMAPplot_",omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]],".pdf)", sep="")
    output_links <- paste(output_links, add_link, sep=" | " )
  })
  
  output_links <- paste(output_links, "  \n", sep="" )
}

output_links <-"";

# If there's a directory called "Subset_Lists" make feature lists based on text files
subset_genes=FALSE;
if( dir.exists("Subset_Lists") ){ try({
  filelist <- list.files(path=file.path("Subset_Lists"), pattern="*.txt")
  subset_genes <- vector("list", length=length(filelist))
  names(subset_genes) <- gsub("*.txt", "", filelist)
  
  for( i in 1:length(filelist)){
    subset_genes[i] <- unique(list(scan(file.path("Subset_Lists", filelist[i]), what="", sep=" " ) ))
  }
}) }

# Correlation for "Genes"
if(length(gene_data_index)>1){ try({
  item_name <- "Gene"
  data_index <- gene_data_index
  
  for (j in 1:length(contrastgroups) ){
    group_name <- paste(item_name,"_", contrastgroups[j], sep="")
    gene_values <- vector("list", (length(data_index)) )
    for (i in 1:(length(data_index)) ){
      group_columns <- grepl(contrastgroups[j], pData(omicsList[[ data_index[i] ]][["eSet"]])$Group)
      gene_values[[i]] <- data.frame( exprs(omicsList[[ data_index[i] ]][["eSet"]])[,group_columns] ); # Make a data frame of values and genes
      gene_values[[i]][,item_name] <- fData(omicsList[[ data_index[i] ]][["eSet"]])[,item_name] ;                                                                         
      gene_values[[i]] <- gene_values[[i]] %>% gather(sample, value, -item_name); # Gather values and get average by gene
      gene_values[[i]] <- gene_values[[i]] %>% group_by(.dots=item_name) %>% summarize(mean=mean(value));
      gene_values[[i]] <- gene_values[[i]][gene_values[[i]][,item_name]!="",]
      names(gene_values)[i] <- paste(omicsList[[ data_index[i] ]][["dataType"]],"_",contrastgroups[j], sep="")
    }
    drawXYCorr(item_list=gene_values, item_name=item_name, file_name = contrastgroups[j] , subset_genes=subset_genes);
    add_link <- paste("[ ",group_name," Correlation Plots ](",output_plots_subdir,"/Correlation_Plots_",group_name,".pdf)", sep="") ;

Correlation Across Groups

output_links <-"";

for(i in 1:length(omicsList)){ try({
  if(length(unique(pData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])$Group))>1){
  gene_values <- data.frame(t(exprs(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])))
  gene_values$Group <- pData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])$Group
  gene_values <- aggregate(. ~ Group, gene_values, mean)
  rownames(gene_values)<- gene_values$Group
  gene_values$Group <- NULL
  gene_values <- data.frame(t(gene_values))
  gene_values$Groups<- row.names(gene_values)
  
  item_list <- vector("list", ncol(gene_values)-1)
  for( j in 1:(ncol(gene_values)-1) ){
    item_list[[j]] <- as_tibble(cbind(gene_values[,"Groups"], gene_values[,j] ), .name_repair="minimal")
    names(item_list[[j]]) <-  c("Groups", colnames(gene_values)[j])
    item_list[[j]][,2] <- as.double(unlist(item_list[[j]][,2]))
  }
  names(item_list)<- colnames(gene_values)[1:(ncol(gene_values)-1)]
  file_name <- omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]]
  item_name <- "Groups"
  drawXYCorr(item_list=item_list, item_name=item_name, file_name=file_name);
  add_link <- paste("[ ",file_name," ](",output_plots_subdir,"/Correlation_Plots_",item_name,"_",file_name,".pdf)", sep="");
  output_links <- paste(output_links, add_link, sep=" | " )
  }
}  ) }

Normalize to 1st Data Set

suppressMessages({suppressWarnings({ 
output_links<-"";
try({
  
# Take first data set for normalization
if(length(prot_data_index)>1){
  item_name <- "Protein"
  data_index <- prot_data_index

  gene_values <- omicsList[[ data_index[1] ]][["eSet"]]; 
  for(i in 2:length(data_index)){
    if( identical(gene_values$SampleName, omicsList[[ data_index[i] ]][["eSet"]]$SampleName) ) {
    
      norm_values <- omicsList[[ data_index[i] ]][["eSet"]] ;
      norm_values <- norm_values[ fData(norm_values)[,item_name] %in% fData(gene_values)[,item_name] ,];
   
    for(g in 1:nrow(norm_values)) {
      gene_values_rows <- grep(fData(norm_values)[g,item_name], fData(gene_values)[,item_name])
      if(length(gene_values_rows)>1){
        gene_values_means <- colMeans(exprs(gene_values)[gene_values_rows,])
      } else {
        gene_values_means <- (exprs(gene_values)[gene_values_rows,])
      }
      exprs(norm_values)[g,] <- (as.numeric(exprs(norm_values)[g,] - gene_values_means )) + mean(gene_values_means) ;
      exprs(norm_values)[g,] <- as.numeric(exprs(norm_values)[g,] + mean(gene_values_means) );
    }
  
    omicsList[[ data_index[i] ]][[10]] <- norm_values;
    names( omicsList[[ data_index[i] ]] )[10] <- "siteNorm";
  
    data_norm_index <- c(data_norm_index, data_index[i]);
    }
  }
} else {
  item_name <- "Gene"
  data_index <- gene_data_index

        gene_values_means <- (exprs(gene_values)[gene_values_rows,])

      exprs(norm_values)[g,] <- as.numeric(exprs(norm_values)[g,] - gene_values_means );
      exprs(norm_values)[g,] <- as.numeric(exprs(norm_values)[g,] + mean(gene_values_means) );
    }

      contrast_strings <- c(contrast_strings, paste(contrastgroups[k],'-',contrastgroups[j], sep=''));
  }  }

  time_index<- length(unique(annot[,"TimeSeries"]))-2;
  time_start <- 3+time_index
  time_end<- 2+(time_index*2)
  loop_list<- time_start:time_end
  new_strings <- c()
  for ( k in 1:length(contrast_strings)){
    for( l in 1:time_index){
      new_strings <- c(new_strings, paste(contrast_strings[k], "_Time_", l, sep=""))

  contrast_strings <- c(new_strings, contrast_strings)

# Limma for DE
for(i in 1:length(omicsList)){ try({
  eset <- omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]]
  IsThereTime <- FALSE; 
  # Create a model matrix and lmFit based on group - For more complex models, edit the following code in this chunk.
  if(time_index>0 ){ try({
    eset<- eset[,which(pData(eset)$Group %in% contrastgroups)]
    f <- factor(pData(eset)$Group, levels=unique(contrastgroups)); 
    Time <- ns(as.numeric(pData(eset)$TimeSeries), df=(time_index))
    design <- model.matrix(~f*Time);
    fit1 <- lmFit( eset, design);
    fit1 <- eBayes(fit1);
    IsThereTime <- TRUE
  }) }
    
  if(IsThereTime == FALSE){
    if("Pairs" %in% colnames(pData(eset)) ){
      f <- factor(pData(eset)$Group)
      p <- factor(pData(eset)$Pairs)
      design <- model.matrix(~p+f);
      fit1 <- lmFit( eset, design);
      fit1 <- eBayes(fit1);
      
      loop_list <- (length(levels(p))+1): ncol(design)
      contrast_strings <- colnames(design)[loop_list]
    } else {
      f <- factor(pData(eset)$Group)#, levels=unique(pData(eset)$Group)); 
      design <- model.matrix(~ 0 + f);
      colnames(design) <- make.names(levels(f));
      fit1 <- lmFit( eset, design);
      contrast_matrix <- makeContrasts(contrasts=contrast_strings, levels=design);
     
      fit1 <- contrasts.fit(fit1, contrast_matrix);
      fit1 <- eBayes(fit1);
    }
  }
  # Summary of the fit
  #end_col <- ncol(topTable(fit1, adjust="BH"))
  #start_col <- end_col - (3+length(contrast_list))
  #print(topTable(fit1, adjust="BH")[,seq(start_col, end_col)])
  
  omicsList[[i]][[7]] <- fit1
  names(omicsList[[i]])[7] <- "fit";
}) }

# Calculate log fold change in case limma fails
logfc_index <- c();
for( i in 1:length(omicsList) ){ try({
  for( j in 1:length(contrastgroups) ){
    if( sum(pData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])$Group==contrastgroups[j])>1 ){
      fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,paste("mean_",contrastgroups[j],sep="")] <- rowMeans(exprs(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,pData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])$Group==contrastgroups[j] ] )
    } else {
      fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,paste("mean_",contrastgroups[j],sep="")] <- exprs(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,pData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])$Group==contrastgroups[j] ] 
    }
  }
  for( j in 1:(length(contrastgroups)-1) ){
    for( k in 2:(length(contrastgroups)) ){
      col_name <- paste("logfc_",contrastgroups[k],"_",contrastgroups[j],sep="");
      fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,col_name] <- ( fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,paste("mean_",contrastgroups[k],sep="")] -
                                                          fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,paste("mean_",contrastgroups[j],sep="")]    ) 
      logfc_index <- c(logfc_index, col_name)
    }
  }
  fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,"MaxFC"] <- apply(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,grep("mean", colnames(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])))], 1, function(x) max(x)/min(x))
}) }

logfc_index <- unique(logfc_index);

# Save data 
for(i in 1:length(omicsList)){ try({
  # Contrasts
  for (c in 1:length(loop_list)){
    top_sum <- FALSE;
    contrast_name <- contrast_strings[c];
    try({ top_sum <- topTable(omicsList[[i]][["fit"]], adjust="BH", n=Inf, sort.by='p', coef=loop_list[c]); })
    if( class(top_sum)=="logical" ){ try({
      top_sum <- data.frame(logFC= fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,paste("logfc_",gsub("-","_",contrast_strings[c]),sep="")],
                          Mean=rowMeans(exprs(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])), 
                          feature_identifier =fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,"feature_identifier"] );
      if( "Gene" %in% colnames(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])) ){ top_sum$Gene <- fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])$Gene }
      if( "mz" %in% colnames(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])) ){ top_sum$mz <- fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])$mz }
    })}
    
    saveFiles(data=omicsList[[i]], limmaRes=top_sum, type=omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]], contrast_name=contrast_name)
    
    if( !( grepl("Human", species) ) & "Gene" %in% colnames(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]]))   ){ 
      top_sum$Gene <- toupper(top_sum$Gene)
      saveFiles(omicsList[[i]], limmaRes=top_sum, type=paste(omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]], "_Uppercase", sep=""), contrast_name=contrast_name)
    }
  }
  
  # MaxFC or F-statistic
  if(statistic_index=='F'){
    top_sum <- FALSE;
    try({ 
      top_sum <- topTableF(omicsList[[i]][["fit"]], adjust="BH", n=Inf, sort.by='F'); 
      top_sum[,"logFC"] <- top_sum[,"F"]
      contrast_name <- "Overall"
      })
    if( class(top_sum)=="logical" ){ try({
      top_sum <- data.frame(logFC= fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,"MaxFC"],
                            Mean=rowMeans(exprs(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])), 
                            feature_identifier =fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])[,"feature_identifier"] );
      if( "Gene" %in% colnames(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])) ){ top_sum$Gene <- fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])$Gene }
      if( "mz" %in% colnames(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])) ){ top_sum$mz <- fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])$mz }
    })}
    
    saveFiles(omicsList[[i]], limmaRes=top_sum, type=omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]], contrast_name=contrast_name)
  
    if(!( grepl("Human", species) ) & "Gene" %in% colnames(fData(omicsList[[i]][["eSet"]])) ){ try({
      top_sum$Gene <- toupper(top_sum$Gene)
      saveFiles(omicsList[[i]], limmaRes=top_sum, type=paste(omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]],"_Uppercase", sep=""), contrast_name=contrast_name)
    }) }
  }
    # TimeSeries
  if(time_index>0){
    top_sum <- FALSE;
    try({ 
      top_sum <- topTable(omicsList[[i]][["fit"]], adjust="BH", n=Inf, sort.by='F', coef=time_start:time_end); 
      top_sum[,"logFC"] <- top_sum[,"F"]
      contrast_name <- "Timecourse_Overall"
    
      saveFiles(omicsList[[i]], limmaRes=top_sum, type=omicsList[[i]][["dataType"]], contrast_name=contrast_name)

      }) }

for(i in 1:length(gene_data_index) ){
  sig_cutoff <- round(sig_percent*nrow(omicsList[[ gene_data_index[i] ]][["eSet"]]), digits=0)
  for(c in 1:length(loop_list) ){ try({
    top_sum<- FALSE;
    contrast_name <- contrast_strings[c]
    try({
      top_sum <- topTable(omicsList[[ gene_data_index[i] ]][["fit"]], adjust="BH", n=Inf, sort.by='p', coef=loop_list[c], p.value=adjpcutoff);
      if (nrow(top_sum)<sig_cutoff){ top_sum <- topTable(omicsList[[ gene_data_index[i] ]][["fit"]], adjust="BH", n=sig_cutoff, sort.by='p', coef=loop_list[c]); }
    })
    if( class(top_sum)=="logical" ){
      top_sum <- data.frame(logFC= fData(omicsList[[ gene_data_index[i] ]][["eSet"]])[,paste("logfc_",gsub("-","_",contrast_strings[c]),sep="")],
                            Gene=fData(omicsList[[ gene_data_index[i] ]][["eSet"]])$Gene, 
                            feature_identifier =fData(omicsList[[ gene_data_index[i] ]][["eSet"]])[,"feature_identifier"] );
      top_sum <- top_sum[top_sum[,"Gene"]!="", ]
      top_sum <- top_sum[order(abs(as.numeric(top_sum[,"logFC"])), decreasing=TRUE),]
      if( nrow(top_sum)>sig_cutoff ){  top_sum <- top_sum[1:sigcutoff,] }
      contrast_name <- gsub("logfc_","",logfc_index[c])
    }
    type_name <- paste(omicsList[[ gene_data_index[i] ]][["dataType"]], contrast_name, sep="_");
    
    runEnrichR(genes=top_sum[, c("Gene", "logFC") ], type=type_name, run_seperate=run_enrichr_seperate) 

  }) } 
  
  # Timecourse
  if(time_index>0){try({
    top_sum<- FALSE;
    contrast_name <- "TimeCourse_Overall"
    top_sum <- topTable(omicsList[[ gene_data_index[i] ]][["fit"]], adjust="BH", n=Inf, coef=time_start:time_end, p.value=adjpcutoff);
    if (nrow(top_sum)<sig_cutoff){ top_sum <- topTable(omicsList[[ gene_data_index[i] ]][["fit"]], adjust="BH", n=sig_cutoff, coef=time_start:time_end); }
    top_sum[,"logFC"] <- top_sum[,'F']
    type_name <- paste(omicsList[[ gene_data_index[i] ]][["dataType"]], "TimeCourse_Overall", sep="_");
    
    runEnrichR(genes=top_sum[, c("Gene", "logFC") ], type=type_name, run_seperate=run_enrichr_seperate) 

  }) } 
}

  } 
   if(statistic_index=='F'){

Metabolite Enrichment

While perhaps the leading tool for metabolite pathway enrichment, the MetaboAnalyst R Package is still in development and work in progress. A recent update creates an error where the metabolic models are not available for download. If this is still the case when your analysis is run, you will see error messages below and no result files created for the metabolite enrichment analysis. In order to complete your analysis, you can take the files that beging with ‘DE_matrix_’ in the /Differential/files/ directory to upload to the MetaboAnalyst website (additional formatting may be required).

rnk_files <-vector("list", num_contrasts)

for (c in 1:num_contrasts){
  for(mumm_lib_index in 1:length(mumm_libs)) { try({
    i <- 1
    analysis_name <- paste(mumm_libs[mumm_lib_index],"_",omicsList[[ metab_data_index[i] ]][["dataType"]],
                           "_",gsub("-","_",contrast_strings[c]), sep="" )
      
    output_mummichog_subdir_tmp <- file.path(output_mummichog_subdir, analysis_name)
    output_mummichog_path_tmp <- file.path(working_dir, output_mummichog_subdir_tmp)
    met_ids <- read.delim(file.path(output_mummichog_path_tmp, "mummichog_matched_compound_all.csv"),
                          header=TRUE, stringsAsFactors = F, sep=",")
  
    met_ranked <- na.omit(topTable(omicsList[[ metab_data_index[i] ]][["fit"]], adjust="BH", n=Inf,
                                   sort.by='p', coef=loop_list[c])[,c("mz", "P.Value", "logFC")] );
    met_ranked[,"rank"] <- ( -log(met_ranked[,"P.Value"]) * sign(met_ranked[,"logFC"]) )
    
    for(n in 1:nrow(met_ids)){
      met_ids[n,"rank"] <- met_ranked[which(met_ids[n,"Query.Mass"] == met_ranked[,"mz"])[1], "rank"]
      
    }
    
    met_ids_out <- met_ids[,c("Matched.Compound", "rank")]
    colnames(met_ids_out) <- c("GeneName", "rank")
    if(length(metab_data_index)>1){
    for(i in 2:length(metab_data_index)){ 
      analysis_name <- paste(mumm_libs[mumm_lib_index],"_",omicsList[[ metab_data_index[i] ]][["dataType"]],
                             "_",gsub("-","_",contrast_strings[c]), sep="" )
      
      output_mummichog_subdir_tmp <- file.path(output_mummichog_subdir, analysis_name)
